Package: mr
Type: Package
Title: Generate Musical Score in R Markdown and RStudio
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Renfei Mao
Maintainer: Renfei Mao <renfeimao@gmail.com>
Description: An elegant and intuitive system for representing musical scores,
    and generating, showing and playing them painlessly in R Markdown and
    RStudio. You only tell "mr" the structure of your music, and it takes care
    of all the dirty technical details.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
Imports:
    base64enc,
    glue,
    htmltools,
    knitr,
    magick,
    magrittr,
    MASS,
    rlang,
    rstudioapi,
    stringr,
    tools,
    utils,
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: MuseScore - https://musescore.org/
